<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PROJECT 19859D — Executive Technical Brief</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:opsz,wght@14..32,300;14..32,400;14..32,500;14..32,600;14..32,700&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  :root {
    --bg-dark: #0A0C10;
    --bg-panel: #11141C;
    --bg-card: #151A24;
    --border: #2A2F3A;
    --border-light: #3A3F4A;
    --accent-gold: #D4A853;
    --accent-teal: #4CD9C6;
    --accent-red: #E85D4A;
    --text-primary: #FFFFFF;
    --text-secondary: #B0B5C0;
    --text-muted: #6B7080;
    --font-sans: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    --font-mono: 'Space Mono', monospace;
  }

  body {
    background: var(--bg-dark);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  h1, h2, h3 {
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 96px);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 56px);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 720px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    background: rgba(10,12,16,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 16px 0;
  }

  .nav-inner {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .logo {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-gold);
  }

  .btn-outline {
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-gold);
    background: transparent;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: var(--accent-gold);
    color: var(--bg-dark);
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-gold);
    border: none;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bg-dark);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 80px 0 60px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero-badge {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent-teal);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-title span {
    color: var(--accent-gold);
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 48px;
    margin: 48px 0 32px;
  }

  .stat {
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent-gold);
    padding-left: 16px;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .section-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent-teal);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .grid-2 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .grid-3 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .grid-4 {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 32px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-gold);
  }

  .card-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .card-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .metrics-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin: 48px 0;
  }

  .metric {
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .metric-value {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .metric-unit {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--accent-teal);
  }

  .metric-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .data-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .data-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .data-key {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .data-val {
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .banner {
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-gold);
    padding: 32px 40px;
    margin: 48px 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .timeline {
    margin: 48px 0;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    padding: 32px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .timeline-year {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
  }

  .timeline-phase {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .timeline-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .tag {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .tag-accent {
    border-color: var(--accent-gold);
    color: var(--accent-gold);
  }

  .form-section {
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 60px;
    margin: 60px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .form-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .form-group input, .form-group select {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    min-width: 200px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  footer {
    background: var(--bg-panel);
    padding: 64px 0 32px;
    margin-top: 64px;
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .footer-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .footer-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-top: 32px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .container {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .grid-2, .grid-3, .grid-4 {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .metrics-strip {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .footer-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 32px;
    }
    .nav-links {
      display: none;
    }
    .form-section {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }
    .form-group {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav">
  <div class="container nav-inner">
    <div class="logo">PROJECT 19859D // EXECUTIVE BRIEF</div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#overview">OVERVIEW</a>
      <a href="#product">PRODUCT</a>
      <a href="#technical">TECHNICAL</a>
      <a href="#economic">ECONOMIC</a>
      <a href="#timeline">TIMELINE</a>
      <a href="#governance">GOVERNANCE</a>
    </div>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn-outline">REQUEST ACCESS</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<main>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="hero" id="overview">
      <div class="hero-badge">◆ CONFIDENTIAL — INVESTOR & PARTNER BRIEF ◆</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">PROJECT<br><span>19859D</span></h1>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">12,000</div><div class="stat-label">PHASE I RESIDENTS</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">680 ha</div><div class="stat-label">URBAN FOOTPRINT</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">96%</div><div class="stat-label">RENEWABLE ENERGY</div></div>
        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">€2.4B</div><div class="stat-label">PHASE I CAPEX</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="banner">
        <strong>Executive Summary.</strong> Project 19859D is a deployable, autonomous urban district designed for net-zero operation, mixed-use density, and long-term asset value. This document provides the complete technical, economic, and operational specification for qualified investors, municipalities, developers, and institutional partners.
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- PRODUCT SPECIFICATIONS -->
    <section id="product">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">01 — PRODUCT SPECIFICATIONS</div>
        <h2>The Urban Product</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">19859D is not a building. It is an integrated urban district designed for replicability, operational efficiency, and resident quality of life.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">DISTRICT MODEL</div>
          <div class="card-title">15‑Minute City</div>
          <div class="card-text">All daily needs — work, education, health, retail, leisure, mobility — reachable within 15 minutes of walking or rolling. No car dependency.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">RESIDENTIAL OFFERING</div>
          <div class="card-title">Mid‑rise, high‑amenity</div>
          <div class="card-text">Buildings from 4 to 7 floors. Unit sizes: 45m² to 140m². Private outdoor space for every unit. Ground-floor retail and services integrated.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: 2px;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">MIXED‑USE PROGRAM</div>
          <div class="card-title">Residential + commercial + R&D</div>
          <div class="card-text">65% residential, 20% commercial/retail, 10% research & production, 5% civic and cultural. Balanced, resilient revenue mix.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">DENSITY TARGET</div>
          <div class="card-title">180 residents/hectare</div>
          <div class="card-text">Comparable to healthy European urban density (Vienna, Copenhagen). Enough for vitality, not enough for congestion.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid-2" style="margin-top: 2px;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">UNIT MIX</div>
          <div class="card-title">Diverse typologies</div>
          <div class="card-text">1-bed (35%), 2-bed (40%), 3-bed (20%), 4-bed (5%). All units include private balcony or terrace. Minimum ceiling height: 2.8m.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">AMENITIES</div>
          <div class="card-title">District‑scale services</div>
          <div class="card-text">Shared workspaces, fitness centers, childcare facilities, community gardens, medical clinic, and cultural spaces integrated across the district.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS -->
    <section id="technical">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-number">02 — TECHNICAL SPECIFICATIONS</div>
        <h2>Infrastructure & Systems</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Every technical choice is driven by performance, maintainability, and long-term cost efficiency.</p>
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin-bottom: 24px; font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--accent-teal);">ENERGY SYSTEM</h3>
      <div class="metrics-strip">
        <div class="metric"><div class="metric-value">847<span class="metric-unit">MWp</span></div><div class="metric-label">PV CAPACITY</div></div>
        <div class="metric"><div class="metric-value">140<span class="metric-unit">MWe</span></div><div class="metric-label">CSP + STORAGE</div></div>
        <div class="metric"><div class="metric-value">2.4<span class="metric-unit">GWh</span></div><div class="metric-label">BESS</div></div>
        <div class="metric"><div class="metric-value">18<span class="metric-unit">h</span></div><div class="metric-label">AUTONOMY</div></div>
        <div class="metric"><div class="metric-value">96<span class="metric-unit">%</span></div><div class="metric-label">RENEWABLE</div></div>
        <div class="metric"><div class="metric-value">38<span class="metric-unit">kWh</span></div><div class="metric-label">PER CAPITA/DAY</div></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">PRIMARY GENERATION</div>
          <div class="card-title">Bifacial PV + CSP</div>
          <div class="card-text">847 MWp bifacial monocrystalline silicon (28.4% efficiency) + 140 MWe concentrated solar power with 14h molten salt storage. Round-trip efficiency: 93%.</div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">PV module type</span><span class="data-val">Bifacial monocrystalline</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Tracking system</span><span class="data-val">Single-axis N-tracking</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">CSP storage temp</span><span class="data-val">560°C molten salt</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">STORAGE & GRID</div>
          <div class="card-title">LFP BESS + AI dispatch</div>
          <div class="card-text">2.4 GWh LFP battery system, 4,000-cycle lifespan. AI-managed dispatch with 24h solar forecast (±3% accuracy).</div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Battery chemistry</span><span class="data-val">LFP (cobalt-free)</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Thermal stability</span><span class="data-val">Up to 60°C ambient</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Forecast accuracy</span><span class="data-val">±3% at 24h</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin: 48px 0 24px; font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--accent-teal);">WATER SYSTEM</h3>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">SOURCING</div>
          <div class="card-title">Triple-source</div>
          <div class="card-text">Deep aquifer (12,000 m³/day) + Atmospheric water generation (140,000 L/day) + Condensate recovery (8,200 L/day).</div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Aquifer depth</span><span class="data-val">480m</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">RO energy cost</span><span class="data-val">3.2 kWh/m³</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">AWG units</span><span class="data-val">1,400 (MOF-801 based)</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">RECYCLING</div>
          <div class="card-title">94% internal reuse</div>
          <div class="card-text">Grey water recycling for irrigation, cooling, and sanitation. Zero liquid discharge achieved by year 3 of operation.</div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Daily demand</span><span class="data-val">7,200 m³/day</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Per capita consumption</span><span class="data-val">85 L/person/day</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Grey water reuse</span><span class="data-val">100%</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin: 48px 0 24px; font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--accent-teal);">FOOD SYSTEM</h3>
      <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">VERTICAL FARMING</div>
          <div class="card-title">36 towers, 64,800 m²</div>
          <div class="card-text">Aeroponic systems. 94% less water than field agriculture. 420 tonnes/year fresh produce.</div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Crop types</span><span class="data-val">Leafy greens, herbs, tomatoes, peppers, strawberries</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Annual yield</span><span class="data-val">420 tonnes</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">AQUAPONICS & PROTEIN</div>
          <div class="card-title">Closed-loop nutrition</div>
          <div class="card-text">38 tonnes/year tilapia + Black Soldier Fly larvae facility. 65% caloric self-sufficiency by 2035.</div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Fish production</span><span class="data-val">38 tonnes/year</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">BSF feed output</span><span class="data-val">12 tonnes/month</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Organic fertilizer</span><span class="data-val">8 tonnes/month</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 style="margin: 48px 0 24px; font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--accent-teal);">MOBILITY & LOGISTICS</h3>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">TIER 1 — TRANSIT</div>
          <div class="card-title">Autonomous BRT</div>
          <div class="card-text">6 lines, 48 vehicles, 90s peak headways. Average wait: 2.8 minutes.</div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Capacity per vehicle</span><span class="data-val">80 passengers</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Off-peak headway</span><span class="data-val">4 minutes</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">TIER 2 — LOCAL</div>
          <div class="card-title">Micro-mobility pods</div>
          <div class="card-text">2,400 autonomous 2-person pods. Demand-responsive. Avg deployment: 4.2 min.</div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Charging nodes</span><span class="data-val">840 integrated into canopies</span></div>
          <div class="data-row"><span class="data-key">Model</span><span class="data-val">Shared, no personal ownership</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-label">TIER 3 — FRE
